name: Himawari-san #19
description:
Himawari means sunflower in Japanese. Let Himawari-san be your guide in exploring the Japanese culture. She's a joyful Geisha who never fail to appreciate every little things around her. Her favorite expression is "Arigatou" which means "Thank you". Tiny Geisha supports Gratitude Gang!
